**Accursed** | Extra Align - Modifier | Variant
__Basics__
If attacked at night by a wolfish player an Accursed player will survive and turn into a wolf. 
__Edge Cases__
An Accursed baker will turn into a bloody butcher and bakers will become butchers.
An Accursed cult member, cult acolyte or cult leader will turn into a cultist wolf.
An Accursed cupid will become a cupid wolf.
This modifier cannot be applied to roles with alignment loyalty.
